Diamond::
"AS far as I know. It does. I have just recently joined them."

::KitKat::
She looks on her wrist monitor that Diamond and the new bots were 
just inside the entrance. She opened her link. "I am KitKat, leader 
of the Predacons. Please fllow Diamond to your quarters and I shall 
meet you shortly."
